Params: {2: 'Lucia', 3: "I'm sorry that we couldn't protect you..."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Lucia, Lee, Commandant, I'm worried about you all, too...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'They were pretty good just now. Nothing suspicious!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Lee clenches his fists and walks forward.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'I finished the mission for you, Watanabe.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "Liv, thanks to your selflessness and courage, we're able to reunite with the imprisoned Forsaken.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Apologies for putting you in danger, Gray Raven...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "In the future, we'll assist Gray Raven to the best of our ability whenever you are operating in the area.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'On the condition that this applies only to Gray Raven and that you will not threaten us Forsaken...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "My answer is no... But we're open to discussion.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: "If you don't have any objection, we can send you to a base that's actually safe.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'There you can also stock up as you please, or choose to leave.', 4: '1'}
